<DocsLayout title="Architecture">
  <h1>Architecture</h1>
  <p>
    EncodeSwarmr is a distributed video encoding orchestration system built around a Controller-Agent model. The Controller is a single Go binary that owns all state; Agents are lightweight worker processes that run on encoding machines and communicate with the Controller over mTLS gRPC.
  </p>

